description:
A Material 3 YouTube Music client for Android A Material 3 YouTube Music client for Android
Features: - Play songs from YT/YT Music without ads - Background playback - Search songs, videos, albums, and playlists from YouTube Music - Library management - Cache and download songs for offline playback - Synchronized lyrics - Skip silence - Audio normalization - Dynamic theme - Localization - Android Auto support - Personalized quick picks - Material 3
